Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.73,0:02:03.90,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,岛津…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.62,0:02:09.49,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,别小看岛津啊…
