Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.48,0:03:04.52,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,丰久
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.52,0:03:05.52,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,撤退吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.27,0:03:07.90,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,伯父 请撤退吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.94,0:03:11.90,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这里就交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.19,0:03:17.66,Drifters Top,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(314.4,175.2)\fad(420,500)}西军
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.19,0:03:17.66,Drifters Top,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(172.8,451.2)\fad(420,500)\be15}岛津兵库头义弘
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.49,0:03:14.57,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你说啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.65,0:03:19.16,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你也要一起回去萨摩的啊 丰久
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.99,0:03:23.70,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想回去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.83,0:03:26.75,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,而且就算死也想死在萨摩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.09,0:03:31.17,Drifters Top,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(354,489)}岛津中务少辅丰久
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.42,0:03:30.80,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,如果伯父一个人能够返回萨摩的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.00,0:03:34.13,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,就算我和士兵们都死了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.55,0:03:38.43,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这一战 也是我们岛津的胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.89,0:03:46.94,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,士兵们 准备射击
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.02,0:03:49.69,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,现已为赴死之时
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.24,0:03:59.91,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人是德川井伊的赤甲部队
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.20,0:04:01.99,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,作为对手来说并不赖
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.66,0:04:05.71,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,赴死战斗的时刻正是现在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.04,0:04:10.29,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,如果把那些家伙活生生地放回萨州的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.58,0:04:12.42,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是德川井伊之耻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.63,0:04:13.17,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.34,0:04:20.18,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,来争分夺秒吧 多一秒是一秒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.18,0:04:23.14,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,把敌人拖延住 能留住一人是一人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.85,0:04:29.90,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我等着你啊 丰久
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.15,0:04:32.65,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我会在萨摩等着你的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.94,0:04:39.57,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我会等着你的 我不允许你死掉啊 丰久
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.70,0:04:41.53,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个好伯父啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.78,0:04:43.78,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,丰久十分幸福啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.62,0:04:49.67,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 就在这里先废掉第一队骑兵的活动能力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.17,0:04:51.13,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,装弹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.25,0:04:53.46,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,瞄准
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.13,0:04:56.09,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,射击
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.72,0:04:59.59,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,别动摇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.97,0:05:00.97,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,继续冲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.69,0:05:17.65,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,真是厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.69,0:05:21.16,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,岛津中务少辅丰久 参上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.20,0:05:27.50,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,将死之兵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.79,0:05:32.33,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,井伊兵部少辅直政 参上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.25,0:05:35.34,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你们可是已经输了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.80,0:05:47.39,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你的项上人头归作我的战利品吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.02,0:05:51.23,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说些什么啊 你个死混球
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.48,0:05:55.77,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,脑袋被砍的人不是我 而是你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.03,0:06:02.86,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,保护直政大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.04,0:06:11.66,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,正好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.42,0:06:19.09,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这…这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.84,0:06:26.14,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,真是蠢蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.31,0:06:38.94,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你才是蠢蛋啊 井伊直政
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.99,0:06:45.53,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈 我做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.16,0:06:50.79,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.79,0:06:51.54,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.66,0:06:52.41,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.71,0:06:53.96,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,直政大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.14,0:07:14.14,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.27,0:07:15.35,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.10,0:07:18.02,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.11,0:07:23.78,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 等等啊 直政
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.86,0:07:26.74,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,开什么玩笑啊 你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.16,0:07:28.45,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,留下你的人头啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.49,0:07:34.16,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,留下你的人头啊 直政
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.98,0:08:04.03,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我要回去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.15,0:08:08.36,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,回到萨摩去
