Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.88,0:08:24.38,Drifters Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz345.5\pos(645.6,426.6)}关原之战
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.88,0:08:24.38,Drifters Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz341.2\pos(624,548.7)}结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.41,0:08:52.24,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,下一个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.33,0:09:07.13,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 什么 这里是哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.26,0:09:10.05,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.26,0:09:15.26,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.89,0:09:20.23,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是要回去的 回到萨摩去的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.26,0:09:49.09,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,下一个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.76,0:09:53.76,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？这里是什么地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.11,0:10:10.11,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.83,0:10:20.04,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 哥哥 死在路边的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.46,0:10:24.17,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事 他居然浑身都是血
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.67,0:10:29.00,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你怎么了 没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.01,0:10:33.93,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧  你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.09,0:10:36.76,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥 这个人是无耳的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.02,0:10:44.35,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,见鬼了啊 果然到地狱了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.02,0:10:46.06,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.19,0:10:48.23,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不是单纯的路人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.36,0:10:51.65,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,根据他的言语 他应该是『漂流者』
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.86,0:10:56.20,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,唉？又是？怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.53,0:11:00.29,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你要我说怎么办… 只好带回去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.45,0:11:01.91,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,带回废城里…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.05,0:11:12.97,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,好重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.14,0:11:20.39,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,实在太重了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.22,0:11:23.14,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不搬快点的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.06,0:11:28.48,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,如果给领主大人看到的话 事情就变得严重了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.86,0:11:30.57,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,停下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.23,0:11:34.45,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,如果再靠近这座城的话就杀了你们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.57,0:11:38.49,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,敢回头或者大声呼喊也杀了你们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.66,0:11:43.58,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你们有何贵干
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.41,0:11:49.00,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你们的伙伴啊 这个人好像快要死的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.54,0:11:51.67,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,亏我们把他带到这里来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.75,0:11:54.26,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,说话再慢一点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.38,0:11:57.01,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我听不清 还有声音太小了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.18,0:11:59.22,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不放慢语速也杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.60,0:12:02.43,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,他和你们一样都是漂流者对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.56,0:12:04.68,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你看 这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.77,0:12:05.64,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.56,0:12:09.27,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,把他留在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.27,0:12:13.69,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,一如既往地不明所以
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.78,0:12:16.20,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,已经够了 快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.03,0:12:21.20,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不仅跑到森林来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.37,0:12:23.83,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,还遇见了漂流者 被发现了肯定会被杀死的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.95,0:12:25.79,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,快回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.46,0:12:30.29,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,武士
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.54,0:12:32.25,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,日本人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.84,0:12:35.13,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,究竟是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.63,0:12:37.93,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,发生了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.09,0:12:40.89,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,有村民抬了个人过来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.18,0:12:42.64,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是日本人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.85,0:12:44.60,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不知是哪一位大名旗下的武士
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.89,0:12:47.06,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,还活着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.68,0:12:49.14,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,已经奄奄一息了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.19,0:12:50.52,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不过还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.27,0:12:53.07,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.69,0:12:56.28,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然没什么象样的药还是给他处理一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.53,0:12:59.40,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,命硬运气好的话或许还能活下来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.74,0:13:07.16,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,就像我们一样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.87,0:13:12.50,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这个尘世实在是太有趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.21,0:13:18.63,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,丰久 丰久
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.63,0:13:21.93,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,初次上战场就能砍下敌将脑袋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.01,0:13:24.93,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,了不起 了不起的青年啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.01,0:13:25.89,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.89,0:13:26.77,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,丰久
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.39,0:13:31.52,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲 父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.27,0:13:33.98,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 你醒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.86,0:13:37.44,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你还真是命大
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.82,0:13:39.07,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,伤口刚刚才缝好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.28,0:13:40.86,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,随便乱动可是会死的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.24,0:13:45.62,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁 你到底是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.74,0:13:48.41,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,谁？ 我才要问你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.79,0:13:52.17,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.29,0:13:55.46,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你是哪里来的什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.00,0:13:58.21,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,木瓜纹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.84,0:14:01.01,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你是织田的家臣吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.38,0:14:02.59,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,家臣？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.22,0:14:04.97,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你说话注意点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.31,0:14:07.72,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是织田
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.89,0:14:09.47,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,织田就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.06,0:14:11.52,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.85,0:14:18.03,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是织田前右府信长
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.73,0:14:17.98,Drifters Top,,0,0,0,,{\fad(420,0)\pos(504,458.4)}织田前右府信长
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.15,0:14:22.65,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,真危险呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.82,0:14:24.16,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.16,0:14:26.91,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你才是蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.95,0:14:28.37,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你说你是信长？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.45,0:14:31.33,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,信长公在很久以前就死了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.37,0:14:35.67,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,果然这里就是阴间
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.96,0:14:40.80,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,而你就是自称信长的阴间小鬼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.39,0:14:47.47,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.18,0:14:51.64,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你醒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.90,0:14:57.90,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,极好极好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.90,0:15:03.90,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,快来 拔毛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.12,0:15:10.20,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你要帮忙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.25,0:15:13.91,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,拔毛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.54,0:15:19.67,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这到底是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.22,0:15:28.55,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你说了信长已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.22,0:15:32.35,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,果然世人都觉得我已经死了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.60,0:15:34.31,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 死了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.56,0:15:38.27,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,在京都本能寺里遭到明智的背叛而被杀死
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.36,0:15:41.40,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这已经是十八年前的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.53,0:15:42.53,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.03,0:15:44.57,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.65,0:15:46.66,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你说十八年前
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.78,0:15:49.07,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那秃子入侵本能寺
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.20,0:15:53.79,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,还有我被丢到这个世界都只是半年前不到的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.71,0:15:56.71,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我才说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.17,0:16:00.71,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你就是阴间的小鬼或者亡魂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.29,0:16:03.67,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不然的话 实在是太荒谬了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.02,0:16:17.48,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,才十年十五年就在大吵大闹的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.52,0:16:20.56,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,从头到尾实在是太好笑太好笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.06,0:16:23.44,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.36,0:16:27.74,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你就告诉他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.95,0:16:29.74,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我是与一
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.99,0:16:34.95,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那须资隆与一正是在下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.20,0:16:34.70,Drifters Top,,0,0,0,,{\fad(350,0)\pos(554.4,504)}那须资隆与一
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.08,0:16:36.71,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,骗子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.16,0:16:38.92,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是源平合战时的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.12,0:16:41.21,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,都四百年前的事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.42,0:16:44.21,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,谁会信你这大话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.21,0:16:48.80,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,即使你说这是谎言
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.18,0:16:52.18,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,但我就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.01,0:16:55.93,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我肯定是在做梦 肯定是在做梦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.60,0:16:57.56,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,然后
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.35,0:17:00.65,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你又是哪里来的什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.86,0:17:02.73,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,岛津
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.73,0:17:04.94,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,岛津丰久
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.36,0:17:07.24,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,岛津家久之子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.61,0:17:08.90,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,岛津
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.53,0:17:10.66,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.07,0:17:15.99,Drifters Normal,,0,0,0,,{\frz339.3\pos(453.6,951.9)}岛津
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.99,0:17:16.37,Drifters Normal,,0,0,0,,{\move(453.6,947.1,974.4,719.1,24,370)}{\frz339.3\pos(453.6,951.9)}岛津
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.37,0:17:22.38,Drifters Normal,,0,0,0,,{\frz340.8\pos(974.4,719.1)}岛津
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.36,0:17:15.24,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里 哪里…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.87,0:17:22.38,Drifters Normal,,0,0,0,,{\frz343.2\pos(1291.2,697.5)}这里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.83,0:17:18.66,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,九州岛的最边边啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.79,0:17:20.46,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,很偏远的乡下地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.50,0:17:22.58,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.79,0:17:25.42,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,岛津大人的话我也认识
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.84,0:17:27.96,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,在我的那个时代已经存在了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.13,0:17:31.59,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,的确是在九州岛的最偏远地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.64,0:17:35.39,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,每一代都是乡下人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.47,0:17:36.97,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我要杀了你们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.18,0:17:39.89,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,活动得太激烈的话会丢掉性命的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.64,0:17:42.73,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,因为那是刚刚才缝好的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.90,0:17:44.40,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你的命真硬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.65,0:17:46.65,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,坐下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.86,0:17:50.70,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你说你是信长对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.32,0:17:54.53,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是死在本能寺了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.83,0:17:56.28,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你应该已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.49,0:18:00.46,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不会被那个秃子杀死呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.46,0:18:03.50,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,边想着要逃出那里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.58,0:18:06.55,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,边带着森兰丸在本能寺内找出口
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.21,0:18:09.46,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不会死在这里啊 混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.71,0:18:12.09,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这边都已经习惯被别人背叛了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.14,0:18:16.85,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,然后就出现在一个奇怪的「地方」了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.01,0:18:19.35,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,用些奇怪的石头做成的过道上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.56,0:18:22.39,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,墙边镶嵌着无数的门在上面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.73,0:18:25.94,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那个奇怪的男人就出现在那条通道的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.73,0:18:27.69,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,正中央
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.40,0:18:33.66,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.78,0:18:35.78,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我也见过那个男人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.37,0:18:38.79,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我也遇见过那个男人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.12,0:18:42.37,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,在关原合战的撤退路上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.42,0:18:44.83,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,关原
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.50,0:18:46.54,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,美浓吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.59,0:18:47.29,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.38,0:18:49.71,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,德川军与石田军之间的大战啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.92,0:18:51.30,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.42,0:18:53.97,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下 等一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.22,0:18:56.01,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,石田不是那个端茶的小子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.09,0:18:58.47,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会和德川在那里开战
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.56,0:18:59.47,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你还说为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.68,0:19:02.81,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,在关白死后天下又变回战国时期了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.85,0:19:03.98,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你说关白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.10,0:19:07.02,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么关白可以夺得天下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.19,0:19:09.48,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为关白大人他一统了天下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.52,0:19:11.28,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,关白秀吉公
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.40,0:19:12.57,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.65,0:19:16.78,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么那只秃头老鼠可以夺得天下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.82,0:19:18.83,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 好烦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.08,0:19:23.04,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,明智死了 柴田也死了 秀吉他就
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.12,0:19:24.37,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,夺得了天下了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.75,0:19:27.29,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,胜家死了吗 阿市呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.96,0:19:28.38,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}兄长大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.08,0:19:28.79,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.00,0:19:31.84,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,丹羽呢 一益呢 利家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.88,0:19:33.26,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.42,0:19:35.97,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,织田家族现在只是帮家康端茶递水的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.13,0:19:38.43,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,天下布武什么的已经没人记得了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.47,0:19:39.51,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.35,0:19:44.73,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,信忠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.94,0:19:48.06,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我的儿子 他怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.65,0:19:50.52,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,死了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.11,0:19:53.19,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,二条城受到了光秀的进攻
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.99,0:19:55.40,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,他认为你已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.90,0:19:57.82,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,就死守在二条城里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.91,0:19:59.87,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,直至到他战死为止
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.87,0:20:05.66,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我愚蠢的儿子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.79,0:20:07.92,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,真蠢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.83,0:20:09.88,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,真蠢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.25,0:20:16.38,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,明明赶紧逃走就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.10,0:20:22.97,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,人生五十载
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.35,0:20:27.52,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我的五十载都是白费的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.40,0:20:30.44,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,世事无情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.02,0:20:33.98,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是从信长大人口中得知
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.03,0:20:38.20,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,源家灭亡 镰仓幕府已经不复存在的时候
